'''Victory Lake''' was a tranquil blue [[lake]] located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="BTS">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref> Fifteen kilometers from [[Imperial City|Galactic City]], the lake served as a reservoir for the [[Capital/Legends|capital]].<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|III|305|Victory Lake}}</ref>

[[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Ackbar]] had a [[Admiral Ackbar's residence|house there]], under and above the [[Water/Legends|water]] near the grassy shore.<ref name="BTS" /> Admiral [[Hiram Drayson/Legends|Hiram Drayson]] also resided on the lake's north shore.<ref name="TT">''[[Tyrant's Test]]''.</ref>

